name: NSFW Commands
description: Enables the usage of nsfw commands (in nsfw channels) in this server.

name: Default Yiff Type
description: Changes the default type returned with the `yiff` command. Valid: **gay**, **straight**, **lesbian**, **dickgirl**

name: Announce Level Increases
description: Sends a message to the channel when someone levels up (f!rank)

name: F Response
description: Replies with "X has paid respects" every time "f" or "rip" is said.

name: Command Images
description: Displays images on some commands in the fun category.

name: Delete Mod Commands
description: Toggles deleting the invocation of moderation commands after execution.

name: Mute Role
description: Sets the role to give to people when they are muted.

name: Modlog Channel
description: Sets the channel to send modlog entries to (also enables the modlog).

name: Language
description: Sets the language the bot will use in this server (english only currently).

name: Economy Emoji
description: Changes the emoji used in economy commands.

name: Welcomer
description: Sends a message when people join this server.

name: Welcome Message Channel
description: The channel to send join messages to.

name: Welcome Message Text
description: Changes the text used in join messages. [formatting](https://botapi.furry.bot/note/welcomer_formatting)

name: Leaver
description: Sends a message when people leave this server.

name: Leave Message Channel
description: The channel to send leave messages to.

name: Leave Message Text
description: Changes the text used in leave messages. [formatting](https://botapi.furry.bot/note/welcomer_formatting)

name: Join/Leave Delete Time
description: Changes the time (in seconds) in which join/leave messages will self destruct (0 to disable).

name: Announce Level Increases
description: Sends a message to the channel when someone levels up (f!rank)
